Paper: hep-th/9410176

Date: 1994-10-24

Title: Entropy Production via Particle Production

Authors: J. Rau

Comments: 4 pages REVTeX

I critically examine the notion of ``irreversibility,'' and discuss in whatsense it applies to the spontaneous creation of particles in external fields.The investigation reveals that particle creation in very strong fields can onlybe described by a non-Markovian transport theory.